What makes Focus Bear different from these apps?

Focus Bear is not just about blocking distractions, it actually helps you through your daily routine. Most other apps just block websites, but Focus Bear has structure and good habits into you day 

If you were a user, why would you choose Focus Bear over competitors?

I will use focus Bear if I want something that could help me stay productibe and take care of myself. It is not just stay away from distractions, it also reminds me to take a break and stay balanced.

What’s one feature that other apps have that Focus Bear doesn’t?

Apps like Tiimo and Routnery show your entire day for the timeline, but Focus Bear does not have that kind of visual schedule yet.

Based on your research, what’s one improvement you think Focus Bear could make?

It would be great if Focus Bear could have a daily planner view to help put my routines and tasks in one place
